1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,602
-As you know,
tonight is the season finale.

2
00:00:02,602 --> 00:00:06,839
Here to reflect on Season 51
is The Hunchback
of 30 Rock herself,

3
00:00:06,839 --> 00:00:08,987
Sarah Sherman.

4
00:00:12,161 --> 00:00:16,257
-Hey, Colin. You know,
this season has made
me finally accept

5
00:00:16,257 --> 00:00:18,188
something
I've been fighting for years.

6
00:00:18,188 --> 00:00:20,888
My haters are right --
It's bad.

7
00:00:20,888 --> 00:00:23,983
-Your acting in sketches?
-No. Hey!

8
00:00:23,983 --> 00:00:26,393
My haircut.
I mean, look at this thing.

9
00:00:26,393 --> 00:00:29,916
Vegan in the front.
Pronouns in the back.

10
00:00:29,916 --> 00:00:35,421
I actually copied this hair
from Paul McCartney's Wings era.

11
00:00:38,418 --> 00:00:42,817
I told him
that in the hallway earlier,
and the strangest thing
happened.

12
00:00:42,817 --> 00:00:45,429
He killed himself.

13
00:00:45,429 --> 00:00:50,351
-Okay.
Sarah, why don't you just cut
your hair then?

14
00:00:50,351 --> 00:00:53,989
-I try, but it always
bounces right back
into this Smollett.

15
00:00:53,989 --> 00:00:57,001
-Smollett?
Is that like a small mullet?

16
00:00:57,001 --> 00:00:58,665
-No, like a Jussie Smollett.

17
00:00:58,665 --> 00:01:03,311
Because it's a hate crime
I did to myself for attention.

18
00:01:05,055 --> 00:01:07,640
-Really good. Really good.

19
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,412
I have to ask --
Who cuts your hair?

20
00:01:09,412 --> 00:01:12,457
-Obviously
Parkinson's Scissorhands.

21
00:01:12,721 --> 00:01:16,883
This haircut's, like, a thing.
It's very popular
with annoying people.

22
00:01:16,883 --> 00:01:19,727
Sorry. I mean
bisexuals in my neighborhood.

23
00:01:19,729 --> 00:01:22,158
By the way, I'm "bye-sexual."

24
00:01:22,158 --> 00:01:27,862
As in "Bye, sex.
You'll never see
me having that with a woman."

25
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:36,535
-What...
What neighborhood do
you live in?

26
00:01:36,535 --> 00:01:40,157
-The part of Brooklyn
where all the white people
do land acknowledgments,

27
00:01:40,157 --> 00:01:44,412
like, "I acknowledge that
I've landed an awesome apartment

28
00:01:44,412 --> 00:01:47,459
that used to belong to
a Puerto Rican family."

29
00:01:50,521 --> 00:01:55,451
-Well, I will say, Sarah,
you look much better
in a wig.

30
00:01:55,451 --> 00:01:57,289
Every time
you're blond in a sketch,

31
00:01:57,289 --> 00:02:01,722
I get more bricked than
the third little pig's house.

32
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:07,911
So then I hit the bathroom,
and I huff and puff

33
00:02:07,911 --> 00:02:10,775
and I blow my own back out.

34
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:16,418
-Jesus, Colin.
God.

35
00:02:16,418 --> 00:02:20,620
Listen, I can put on a wig,
but I still have
a resting mullet face.

36
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:22,827
And to prove it,
here's a compilation

37
00:02:22,827 --> 00:02:27,881
of men pulling away
from my unscripted kisses.

38
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:48,393
Damn.

39
00:02:48,393 --> 00:02:52,288
Don't clap.
Pathetic. Do not clap.

40
00:02:52,288 --> 00:02:57,702
Matt Damon dodged me
like he was George Bush
and I was the shoe.

41
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:01,752
-Oh, my God.
Well, timely reference.

42
00:03:01,752 --> 00:03:05,465
You know, Sarah,
you have to stop being so hard
on yourself, you know?

43
00:03:05,465 --> 00:03:08,696
-You're right, you're right.
I'll keep my hair the way it is.

44
00:03:08,696 --> 00:03:10,324
Oh, shut up!

45
00:03:10,324 --> 00:03:13,393
And, hey, thanks for being sweet
to me, Colin.

46
00:03:13,393 --> 00:03:17,407
How about we end this season
with a kiss?

47
00:03:19,381 --> 00:03:24,742
Oh! Pepper...
Pepper spray!

48
00:03:24,742 --> 00:03:26,875
-Sarah and her mullet,
everyone.

49
00:03:26,875 --> 00:03:28,342
Get the hell out!

